      "comment": "LUCKY SPEECH (4) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better over 1609m at Sam Houston Park Turf, beaten 2.5 lengths after being in contention on the bend. Well placed and there is no reason she cannot find winning ways. TIZAWIZ (2) finished second when resuming two runs back at Sam Houston Park Turf (Turf) then progressed nicely last time out to score by 4 lengths as public elect over 1609m at Sam Houston Park Turf (Turf). This looks a sterner test than last time but on current form she is capable of another big performance. MULTIPLICATION (1) returns from a layoff of ten weeks. Worth noting she filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last prep over 1609m at Churchill Downs Turf. One to consider. TIZ THE SPIRIT (6) transitions to a turf track for the first time. Unbeaten in two runs this campaign, winning when fresh over 1308m at Sunland Park then again saluting last time over 1308m at Sunland Park. Should park just off the speed. Don't underestimate.",
